      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CAWBOURNE OZZY (1) was in traffic and failed to finish last start but the start prior was a Grade 4 winner in the quickest time on the card at Goulburn in a Grade 4. Should be in this for a long way. TIGGERLONG SNOW (4) is a progressive type who recorded his 6th career win last time out (18.93) at this track. Hard to go past form at this journey. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. WESTSIDE STORM (2) missed the frame last time when fourth (19.25) at this track but prior to that had two placings in a row. Solid record at the distance winning 14 races. Likely to be about the mark. KILLER FORGE (7) scored last time and appeals as a top-three prospect.",
